                'description' => '<p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed"><strong>Emergency Escape Breathing Apparatus (EEBD). Certified Respiratory Protection for Marine Emergency Evacuation.</strong></p><p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed">The <strong>Emergency Escape Breathing Apparatus (EEBD)</strong> is a certified, self-contained respiratory device designed to provide breathable air during emergency evacuations from smoke-filled or oxygen-deficient spaces aboard vessels. Compact, lightweight, and fast to don, it gives crew members the critical minutes needed to safely escape hazardous environments. Certified by both <strong>CCS and CE</strong>, it meets international maritime safety standards.</p><h2 class="mt-12 mb-6 text-xl font-semibold text-cyan-600">Components</h2><div class="mb-12 rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-slate-200"><div class="grid grid-cols-12 bg-cyan-600 text-white text-sm font-semibold px-4 py-3"><div class="col-span-1 text-center">#</div><div class="col-span-11">Component</div></div><div class="grid grid-cols-12 items-center px-4 py-3 bg-white border-b border-slate-100 text-slate-700 text-sm"><div class="col-span-1 text-center font-semibold text-cyan-600">1</div><div class="col-span-11"><span class="font-medium">Full Face Mask</span><p class="text-slate-500 text-xs mt-0.5">Provides a complete airtight seal over the face, protecting eyes, nose, and mouth from smoke and toxic gases</p></div></div><div class="grid grid-cols-12 items-center px-4 py-3 bg-slate-50 border-b border-slate-100 text-slate-700 text-sm"><div class="col-span-1 text-center font-semibold text-cyan-600">2</div><div class="col-span-11"><span class="font-medium">Cylinder Bag</span><p class="text-slate-500 text-xs mt-0.5">Durable carrying bag for secure storage and quick deployment of the gas cylinder</p></div></div><div class="grid grid-cols-12 items-center px-4 py-3 bg-white border-b border-slate-100 text-slate-700 text-sm"><div class="col-span-1 text-center font-semibold text-cya