                'image'       => '/images/products/self-contained.png',
                'description' => '<p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed"><strong>Self-Contained Breathing Apparatus (S.C.B.A.). Certified Positive-Pressure Respiratory Protection for Marine Firefighting and Hazardous Operations.</strong></p><p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed">The <strong>Self-Contained Breathing Apparatus (S.C.B.A.)</strong> is a certified, positive-pressure respiratory protection system designed for use in firefighting, rescue operations, and entry into oxygen-deficient or toxic atmospheres aboard vessels. Unlike the EEBD which is for escape only, the S.C.B.A. is built for <strong>active operations in immediately dangerous environments</strong>, delivering a continuous supply of clean, pressurized air to the wearer. Certified by both <strong>CCS and CE</strong>, it meets the highest international maritime safety standards.</p><h2 class="mt-12 mb-6 text-xl font-semibold text-cyan-600">Components</h2><div class="mb-12 rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-slate-200"><div class="grid grid-cols-12 bg-cyan-600 text-white text-sm font-semibold px-4 py-3"><div class="col-span-1 text-center">#</div><div class="col-span-11">Component</div></div><div class="grid grid-cols-12 items-center px-4 py-3 bg-white border-b border-slate-100 text-slate-700 text-sm"><div class="col-span-1 text-center font-semibold text-cyan-600">1</div><div class="col-span-11"><span class="font-medium">Full Face Mask</span><p class="text-slate-500 text-xs mt-0.5">Wide-view, airtight face piece providing full protection of eyes, nose, and mouth from smoke, toxic gases, and hazardous atmospheres</p></div></div><div class="grid grid-cols-12 items-center px-4 py-3 bg-slate-50 border-b border-slate-100 text-slate-700 text-sm"><div class="col-span-1 text-center font-semibold text-cyan-600">2</div><div class="col-span-11"><span class="font-medium">Backing</span><p class="text-slate-500 text-xs mt-0.5">Ergonomic back frame and harness assembly for secure, comfortable carrying of the cylinder during extended operations</p></div></div><div class="grid grid-cols-12 items-center px-4 py-3 bg-white border-b border-slate-100 text-slate-700 text-sm"><div class="col-span-1 text-center font-semibold text-cyan-600">3</div><div class="col-span-11"><span class="font-medium">Gas Cylinder</span><p class="text-slate-500 text-xs mt-0.5">High-pressure cylinder containing compressed breathable air, rated for sustained use during firefighting and rescue operations</p></div></div><div class="grid grid-cols-12 items-center px-4 py-3 bg-slate-50 border-b border-slate-100 text-slate-700 text-sm"><div class="col-span-1 text-center font-semibold text-cyan-600">4</div><div class="col-span-11"><span class="font-medium">Medium Pressure Pipe Assembly</span><p class="text-slate-500 text-xs mt-0.5">Reduces and regulates air pressure from the cylinder to a safe medium pressure level before delivery to the face mask</p></div></div><div class="grid grid-cols-12 items-center px-4 py-3 bg-white border-b border-slate-100 text-slate-700 text-sm"><div class="col-span-1 text-center font-semibold text-cyan-600">5</div><div class="col-span-11"><span class="font-medium">High-Pressure Connector</span><p class="text-slate-500 text-xs mt-0.5">Robust coupling rated for high-pressure service, ensuring a secure and leak-free connection between the cylinder and the breathing circuit</p></div></div><div class="grid grid-cols-12 items-center px-4 py-3 bg-slate-50 border-b border-slate-100 text-slate-700 text-sm"><div class="col-span-1 text-center font-semibold text-cyan-600">6</div><div class="col-span-11"><span class="font-medium">Positive Pressure Air Control Device</span><p class="text-slate-500 text-xs mt-0.5">Maintains a constant positive pressure inside the face mask, preventing toxic gases from entering even if the seal is momentarily disturbed</p></div></div><div class="grid grid-cols-12 items-center px-4 py-3 bg-white border-b border-slate-100 text-slate-700 text-sm"><div class="col-span-1 text-center font-semibold text-cyan-600">7</div><div class="col-span-11"><span class="font-medium">Pressure Relief Valve Assembly</span><p class="text-slate-500 text-xs mt-0.5">Automatic safety valve that releases excess pressure to protect the system integrity and ensure safe operation under all conditions</p></div></div><div class="grid grid-cols-12 items-center px-4 py-3 bg-cyan-50 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700"><div class="col-span-1"></div><div class="col-span-8 text-cyan-700">Total Components</div><div class="col-span-3 text-right pr-1"><span class="inline-block bg-cyan-600 text-white font-bold text-xs px-3 py-1 rounded-full">7 pcs</span></div></div></div><div class="my-8 bg-cyan-700 text-white rounded-xl p-6 flex gap-4 items-start"><div class="text-3xl mt-1">🔵</div><div><h3 class="text-base font-bold mb-1">Positive Pressure Technology</h3><p class="text-cyan-100 text-sm leading-relaxed">Unlike standard breathing apparatus, the S.C.B.A. uses a <strong class="text-white">positive pressure system</strong> that continuously pushes clean air outward inside the mask. This ensures that even under physical stress or an imperfect seal, <strong class="text-white">no toxic air can enter</strong> — a critical safety advantage during active firefighting operations.</p></div></div><h2 class="mt-12 mb-6 text-xl font-semibold text-cyan-600">Key Features</h2><ul class="mb-12 space-y-2 text-slate-700"><li class="pl-6 py-1.5 border-l-4 border-cyan-400 bg-slate-50/50"><strong class="block font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Positive Pressure Operation:</strong> Prevents any toxic gas infiltration into the face mask, even under demanding conditions</li><li class="pl-6 py-1.5 border-l-4 border-cyan-400 bg-slate-50/50"><strong class="block font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Full Face Coverage:</strong> Wide-view face mask provides complete facial protection and clear visibility during operations</li><li class="pl-6 py-1.5 border-l-4 border-cyan-400 bg-slate-50/50"><strong class="block font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Ergonomic Back Frame:</strong> Backing harness distributes cylinder weight evenly for extended wear comfort</li><li class="pl-6 py-1.5 border-l-4 border-cyan-400 bg-slate-50/50"><strong class="block font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Dual-Stage Pressure Regulation:</strong> High-pressure connector and medium pressure pipe assembly work together for precise, safe air delivery</li><li class="pl-6 py-1.5 border-l-4 border-cyan-400 bg-slate-50/50"><strong class="block font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Dual Certified:</strong> Approved by both CCS and CE, compliant with SOLAS and international LSA code requirements</li></ul><h2 class="mt-12 mb-6 text-xl font-semibold text-cyan-600">Certifications</h2><div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mb-12"><span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-cyan-50 border border-cyan-300 text-cyan-800 font-semibold px-5 py-2 rounded-full text-sm">✅ CCS Certified</span><span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-cyan-50 border border-cyan-300 text-cyan-800 font-semibold px-5 py-2 rounded-full text-sm">✅ CE Certified</span></div><div class="mt-6 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-5 text-sm text-slate-700 leading-relaxed"><strong class="block font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">📋 S.C.B.A. vs EEBD — Know the Difference</strong><div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-3 text-xs"><div class="bg-white border border-cyan-200 rounded-lg p-3"><div class="font-bold text-cyan-700 mb-1">S.C.B.A.</div><ul class="space-y-1 text-slate-600"><li>✔ Active firefighting &amp; rescue</li><li>✔ Positive pressure protection</li><li>✔ Extended duration use</li><li>✔ Back-mounted cylinder</li></ul></div><div class="bg-white border border-amber-200 rounded-lg p-3"><div class="font-bold text-amber-700 mb-1">EEBD</div><ul class="space-y-1 text-slate-600"><li>✔ Emergency escape only</li><li>✔ Compact &amp; quick to don</li><li>✔ Short duration use</li><li>✔ Portable cylinder bag</li></ul></div></div></div>',            ],
