            [
                'name'        => 'Drinking Cup Guaranteed',
                'category'    => 'Emergency Life Raft Equipments',
                'image'       => '/images/products/drinking-cup.png',
                'description' => '<p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed"><strong>Drinking Cup. Collapsible Survival Drinking Cup for Life Raft and Marine Emergency Kits.</strong></p><p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed">The <strong>Marine Survival Drinking Cup</strong> is a compact, lightweight cup designed specifically for use in life raft survival kits and emergency grab bags. Intended for the rationing and consumption of fresh water during survival situations at sea, this cup ensures survivors have a practical means of measuring and drinking their limited water supply. A standard required item in <strong>SOLAS Pack A and Pack B</strong> life raft survival kits, it plays a simple but vital role in keeping survivors hydrated throughout an emergency.</p><h2 class="mt-12 mb-6 text-xl font-semibold text-cyan-600">Primary Functions</h2><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-12"><div class="border-2 border-cyan-400 rounded-lg p-5 bg-slate-50"><div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3"><span class="text-2xl">💧</span><h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-base m-0">Water Rationing</h3></div><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Allows survivors to measure and distribute limited freshwater supplies in controlled portions. Proper rationing of drinking water is critical to prolonging survival time during extended periods adrift at sea.</p></div><div class="border-2 border-cyan-400 rounded-lg p-5 bg-slate-50"><div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3"><span class="text-2xl">🛟</span><h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-base m-0">Survival Kit Essential</h3></div><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Designed to pack efficiently within life raft survival kits alongside emergency rations and water supplies. Its compact form ensures it occupies minimal space while remaining immediately accessible when needed.</p></div></div><h2 class="mt-12 mb-6 text-xl font-semibold text-cyan-600">Key Features</h2><ul class="mb-12 space-y-2 text-slate-700"><li class="