ure Range</span><span>-25°C ~ +50°C</span></div></div></div><div class="border-2 border-cyan-400 rounded-xl overflow-hidden"><div class="bg-cyan-600 text-white px-5 py-3"><h3 class="font-bold text-base m-0">Water Fire Extinguisher</h3><p class="text-cyan-200 text-xs mt-0.5">Model: MSQ</p></div><div class="p-5 bg-slate-50 space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-700"><div class="flex justify-between border-b border-slate-100 pb-2"><span class="font-semibold text-slate-900">Capacity</span><span>2L, 6L, 9L</span></div><div class="flex justify-between border-b border-slate-100 pb-2"><span class="font-semibold text-slate-900">Fire Rating</span><span>Class A</span></div><div class="flex justify-between border-b border-slate-100 pb-2"><span class="font-semibold text-slate-900">Range</span><span>≥ 4 m</span></div><div class="flex justify-between border-b border-slate-100 pb-2"><span class="font-semibold text-slate-900">Discharge Time</span><span>30 – 45 s</span></div><div class="flex justify-between border-b border-slate-100 pb-2"><span class="font-semibold text-slate-900">Working Pressure</span><span>10 bar</span></div><div class="flex justify-between"><span class="font-semibold text-slate-900">Temperature Range</span><span>-25°C ~ +50°C</span></div></div></div></div><h2 class="mt-12 mb-6 text-xl font-semibold text-cyan-600">Fire Class Coverage</h2><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-12"><div class="border-2 border-orange-300 rounded-lg p-5 bg-orange-50"><div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3"><span class="text-2xl">🔥</span><h3 class="font-bold text-orange-900 text-base m-0">Class A — Solid Combustibles</h3></div><p class="text-orange-800 text-sm leading-relaxed">Fires involving solid organic materials such as wood, paper, textiles, and plastics. Common in accommodation spaces, storerooms, and deck areas. Covered by <strong>both MJPZ and MSQ</strong>.</p></div><div class="border-2 border-red-300 rounded-lg p-5 bg-red-50"><div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3"><sp