ication:</strong> The 7×50 combination is the internationally recognized standard for marine navigation binoculars</li><li class="pl-6 py-1.5 border-l-4 border-cyan-400 bg-slate-50/50"><strong class="block font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Waterproof &amp; Fog-Proof:</strong> Sealed and nitrogen-purged optics prevent internal fogging and water ingress during marine operations</li></ul>',
